        <p>You can insert images by dragging and dropping the image file from the Content Explorer or File List window pane to the XML Editor.</p>
        <p>With this method, you can specify any necessary advanced settings for that image only after it is inserted (to do this, right-click on the inserted image and select <span class="Emphasis">Image Properties</span>).</p>
